What does the following method return when called with the given array and a target value of 25?
```java
public static int[] findElement(int[][] arr, int target) {
    for (int r = 0; r < arr.length; r++) {
        for (int c = 0; c < arr[r].length; c++) {
            if (arr[r][c] == target) {
                return new int[]{r, c};
            }
        }
    }
    return new int[]{-1, -1};
}
```
